<%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <%- include('../partials/nav') %>

        <main class="faq-main-page">
            <section class="page-title-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                    <p>Everything you need to know to plan your perfect visit to Verdoliva Eco Park.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="faq-content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="faq-wrapper">

                        <details class="faq-item" open>
                            <summary>What are the park's opening hours?</summary>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Verdoliva Eco Park is open daily from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM. Last entry is at 4:30 PM. We recommend arriving early to fully enjoy all the habitats and experiences.</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary>Is there parking available on site?</summary>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Yes! We have a large, eco-friendly parking lot with solar canopies. We also offer dedicated EV charging stations for electric vehicles near the main entrance.</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary>Are the habitats wheelchair accessible?</summary>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>Absolutely. Accessibility is a priority for us. All main pathways, the Rainforest Canopy viewing decks, and our facilities are fully wheelchair accessible.</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary>Can I bring my own food and drinks?</summary>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>You are welcome to bring water bottles and small snacks. However, large picnics and glass containers are not permitted inside the animal habitats for safety reasons. We have a great café on site!</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details class="faq-item">
                            <summary>Do I need to book experiences in advance?</summary>
                            <div class="faq-answer">
                                <p>General admission includes access to all habitats. However, special experiences like the Giraffe Feeding or Nocturnal Canopy Tour have limited spaces and should be booked online prior to your visit.</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>